{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "擅闖者", "storyInfo": "兩個解說員互不相讓地爭辯身分真偽時，高登已經意識到，他放任一個冒牌貨在園區活動了一個月。所幸，冒牌貨只是個導遊，為幫助一位女妖客人才混了進來。另一邊，“幸運瘤獸”的經理按照神秘通話人的指引，來到了高登的秘密收藏室。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g7_airrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "-80,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "-30,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兄弟，要是你真的喜歡這個名字，拿去用也就算了，沒必要剽竊我的人生經歷啊！", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.8, "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼好意思反咬我一口，所有資料和履歷都是我親自寫的！", "name": "奧克里！"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-30,0", "posto": "20,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.8, "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能完全複述一遍嗎？", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#6$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……這都是我一年前寫的東西了，怎麼可能一字不漏！", "name": "奧克里！"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“奧克里，堡壘山人，畢業於特里蒙文理學院，曾在特區會展中心工作，擔任人類發展與技術倉新部門的講解專員……”", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“創新”還寫錯了。", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你！可惡，要不是我弄丟了終端和資料履歷——", "name": "奧克里！"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "高登的頭從來沒有這麼痛過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "再次確認資料後，他一眼就看出了報到流程上的漏洞，但最大的問題不在於此——", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她究竟為什麼要假冒解說員？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她是萊塔尼亞派來刺探科技實力的間諜？受國防部直接命令的情報探子？還是特區政府安插在自己身邊的眼睛？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "預展上，這個冒牌貨已經跟大部分企業有過接觸，現在處理她就等於把自己的疏忽昭告天下。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "更要命的是，高登完全不知道她究竟探聽到了多少消息，是否會對自己不利、對哥倫比亞不利……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登不敢想下去了。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "posfrom": "20,0", "posto": "20,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你說話的時候眼神游移，語無倫次，聲音發抖。", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想以長官的眼光也不會選擇這樣一位“奧克里”擔任宣傳工作吧？", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你少把長官扯進來！我告訴你——", "name": "奧克里！"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都別吵了！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "-150,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "奧克里！"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "posfrom": "280,0", "posto": "140,0", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧克里“先生”，您需要冷靜一下，跟我來吧，我帶您去貴賓室休息。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "140,0", "posto": "80,0", "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "250,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.1}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.1, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "-180,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官，我……", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你給我聽好了，我剛剛調取了你在園區裡的行為記錄，查清你的真實身分也易如反掌。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是再撒一次謊，我會立刻把你從六百多公尺的高空丟下去。不管你是什麼人，最後都會變成地上的一攤爛泥，明白嗎？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說，你是誰。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……解說員……", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有骨氣。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旅、旅行時需要的那種解說員！", "name": "奧克里？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫費爾南，是個……導遊。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧克里先生，真是非常抱歉，高登長官一定會儘快解決這件事，給您一個交代的。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們相信我了？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。有什麼需要您都可以透過這個終端聯絡我，現在我就先不打擾您休息了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": "0", "duration": 1.2}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g14_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞定。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "察言觀色，提前為上司規避風險……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是秘書準則。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g7_airrestaurant", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說，一個月前奧克里失戀喝醉酒，把解說員的履歷當作聯絡方式給了你，正好讓你得以借用他的身分，帶人混進我的園區？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的客人是一位年邁的女妖，不知道為什麼在骸骨荒原迷路了，她記憶模糊，交流起來也很辛苦？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你懷疑她生病了，為了讓她的旅程順心，你只能藉解說員的身分跟人打聽解決方法，所以才顯得心懷不軌？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完全正確！", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在園區待了一個月，知道這裡的特殊性。如果你是其他國家派來的間諜，軍方會拷打你、審問你，讓你再也回不了家。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是國防部的情報專員，特區政府不會放過你，他們會顛倒黑白甚至將你驅逐出境，只為了能爭得更多話語權。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你是特區政府的眼線，那你知道的太多了。我有很多從管理局學來的手段，可以強制讓你“失憶”。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你只是一名體貼遊客的導遊，是一個好人。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而哥倫比亞從不會虧待好人。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官……您不追究我的責任了嗎？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很想追究，但因為你在預展上的表現，許多企業代表已經注意到了你。趁他們查出你的來歷前，你必須處理完自己的問題，馬上滾蛋。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你待得越久，我就要花越多補償金，安撫那個被你頂替的倒楣鬼。如果你只是想讓那位女妖客人恢復清醒，我可以幫你。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道女妖相關的知識？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道怎麼解決你的問題。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g10_ecolab", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.95, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開始接入浮空種植單元。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_activation"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "驅動裝置接收到生物電訊號，正在充能。", "name": "資深研究員"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……最順利的一次實驗，不是嗎？", "name": "資深研究員"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，這個聲音……斷點保護裝置自行啟動了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）解離。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_powerengine_run", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）解離！", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_powerengine_run", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_machinedeath"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.95, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "isblock": "true", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，你怎麼能直接用手處理過載的能源轉換器！", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它比我的咒言更有效。參數如何？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為即將在展覽上披露的成果來看，利用植物進行高空能量傳輸的技術已經成熟，但如果要滿足你對整個計劃的期望……", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不夠，浮空種植單元的能量傳輸閾值還沒到達最初的理論值。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是你在那個炸毛的豐蹄小子面前也這麼說，他就不會整天氣呼呼的了……", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯凱經驗不足，但有一點說得沒錯——這座生態園是克麗斯騰留下的東西，我們必須做到最好。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，五年前我跟你一起在地下建能量井的時候，你就是這麼固執強硬。", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了保證結構強度，你不眠不休地為上萬件核心建材施加咒言，哪怕用你最喜歡的蚯蚓軟糖引誘你去休息都無濟於事。", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "釣鱗應該去蘇里根湖，如果你的請假申請能被我批准的話。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，本來就是因為我的效率太低，才需要不眠不休。我太晚學習咒言，僅以聲音作為媒介，精準程度和強度都會低於同族。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你改造了自己的骨筆，還用打孔紙帶作為施咒的輔助媒介？", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我走了很多彎路。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提拿出自己的骨筆，筆身沒有絲毫裝飾和雕刻，如一件萊茵出品的科技造物。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她將骨筆插進生態園培育的樹苗上，白色的螢光從根部升起，沿著葉脈，流進每一片樹葉。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個生態園彷彿被注入了一道指令，終端程式開始運轉，自動記錄植物能量轉換的相關數據。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_activation"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.3}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 0.0, "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 0.95, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咒言對你而言，還真是一種高效的程式語言……", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那與之相對地，在實驗出現瓶頸的當下，我們也應該做一個有些冒險但更有效率的決定。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任，你是說……", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再去核驗一遍報告吧，辛苦了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "資深研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2051_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephonering"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_telephone"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，萊茵生態園實驗室。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任您好。高登長官想讓我轉達他的謝意，上次能達成合作多虧您的通情達理。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過協議還涉及一些後續事宜需要跟您商談，請問您今天下午有時間嗎？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了，一小時後，我們生態園見。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_elevator", "loop": "true", "channel": "ele", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "ele", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坐纜車，到飛天甜甜圈站下車，再走環形廊道……", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我應該沒找錯地方吧？好黑，燈在哪裡……", "name": "雅斯彭"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g8_gordoncollection", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "ele", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天空保佑……這、這是什麼地方！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$relax_intro", "key": "$relax_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發現入侵者，發現入侵者！", "name": "不明造物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生物掃描開啟，評估基礎資訊：泰拉人，男性，威脅程度待定。", "name": "不明造物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻……會說話的鱗獸？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$2", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知好歹的泰拉人，注意你的言詞！我是太空鱗獸零五四，快報上你的宇宙身分識別碼。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$2"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身分識別碼……？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）就是您的企業名稱。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#3$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦哦，幸運瘤獸餐飲。", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#3$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，原來你就是“天空征服者”命令我接應的合作夥伴，看來不能試驗我的鐳射炮了，可惜。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$3"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）請不要碰任何東西，長官馬上就到。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodfloor_fts", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$6", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "零五四，下次為客戶說明的時候，也要記得用外泰拉生物的方式說話。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遵命。", "name": "太空鱗獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高、高登長官？！", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓——別大呼小叫的。身處這間全泰拉絕無僅有的奇珍異品收藏室，先用眼睛讚嘆才符合禮儀。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2040_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看你右邊那面牆。五年前，一個拓荒者試圖非法越境。收繳所有物時，我在他的移動板房裡發現了一套設計特殊的淨水循環系統。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了將功抵過，他偷偷替我找到了核心部分，組裝後我認出它是“咒術湍流焦點”，一件薩卡茲的巫術武器。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，那一定很危險……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#4$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轉身。這是產自萊塔尼亞的三頭施術單元。一名巫王殘黨想要增加源石技藝的輸出強度，撕裂時空，召喚他們的王。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撕裂時空太過天方夜譚，但它的能源轉換效率遠遠超出園區規定值的五十倍，用它施術之後連洋蔥都能飛起來。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，所以您解決“一隻靴子”的技術問題的方法是……向他們提供違禁品？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#5$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "違禁品？“只能使用哥倫比亞製造的零件”是死板的管理局給“螺旋槳天堂”定下的新規矩！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不懂，也不想揣測背後的原因。我只知道，那些根本不符合哥倫比亞進取精神的規則讓科學家束手束腳，逼得企業家只能說謊！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果呢？是一個小小的管理局官員將來自泰拉各地的發明運入園區，為三分之一的浮空設施安上了心臟。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三分之一……您進行過上百次走私交易，到現在都還沒有暴露過？", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我的管理下，每筆交易、每個環節都順利得不可思議，連經常在我身邊的秘書小梅都不知道我的“秘密”。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官，我還是需要時間考慮……", "name": "雅斯彭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2041_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“幸運瘤獸”的壽命只剩下最後一天，而我接下來還有其他要務需要處理，只能給你，嗯，五秒鐘。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，你是要為“幸運瘤獸”換上一顆雜交的心臟，還是要讓它抱著無聊的、不屬於你的堅持去死？", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}